title: [Surname Registry]
description: Neatly ordered rows of chairs face the front of the room, their wooden backs ramrod-straight.  The walls are decorated with framed genealogy charts, each one beautifully painted with family crests.  Vaalorian flags hang to either side of a large portrait of King Tyrnian.
